setVideoPlayer

public void setVideoPlayer(AROVideoPlayer videoPlayer)
Sets the video player to be used with this AROAdvancedTabb. The video player displays a video of screen captures that were recorded while trace data was being captured. The current time position in the video playback is updated to match the selected time position in the AROAdvancedTabb chart.

Parameters:
videoPlayer - An AROVideoPlayer object representing the video player to be used with this AROAdvancedTabb.
